yingyinNormal.en: Can you be a player/owner?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你会当老板球员吗？
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: There's never been a player/owner, but maybe. Maybe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从来就没有老板球员这种人，不会额可能会吧，有可能。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: No, it's another one, different owner, different part of town.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，是另一个。不同的主人，不同的地点。

yingyinNormal.en: But who told you, you could cut it down? The owner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁批准你们砍树的? 树的主人啊。

yingyinNormal.en: What are you talking about? My old owner and I used to live around here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在说什么？我以前的主人住这附近。

yingyinNormal.en: Nikita stole the car in Vermont. Any chance the owner works in Manhattan?
yingyinNormal.zh: 尼基塔是在佛蒙特州偷的车，车主会不会在曼哈顿工作

yingyinNormal.en: If my owner comes, put on the hood and pretend to be me. Okay, thank you!
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我主人过来，戴上眼罩，假装是我。好的，谢谢！

yingyinNormal.en: Well, if George is owner of half the estate now, shouldn't you represent him?
yingyinNormal.zh: 既然乔治现在拥有一半庄园，难道你不该代表他吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Duke, we gotta go to your house! No. You know, your owner's gonna be relieved.
yingyinNormal.zh: 杜克，咱们要去找你家！不要。你主人会很开心的。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, Sheldon, it took me all morning, but I found the owner of the video store.
yingyinNormal.zh: Sheldon，我花了一上午找到了影音店的老板。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, of course he likes you, he was your owner. I mean he's probably worried sick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他当然喜欢你，他是你的主人。他可能担心疯了。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you think you could fix it? Maybe. Should we try and track down the owner first?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你觉得你能修好吗？或许吧。但我们是不是该先找到主人是谁？

yingyinNormal.en: You know, you could reimburse the video store owner's next of kin. Or it's resolved!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你其实可以还给店老板的后代。或者就这么了结吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm the proud owner of wilwheatonstinks.com, .net, and .org. What does that tell you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可是“臭威尔惠顿”企业网站，互联网站和机构网站的所有人，知道这说明什么吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Congratulations. You are the proud owner of a miniature time machine. You lucky duck.
yingyinNormal.zh: 祝贺你你光荣地成为这台小型时间机器的主人了。你个幸运的家伙。

yingyinNormal.en: Owners of ticket and non-owner of the ticket, that are not different in any other way.
yingyinNormal.zh: 得到票的人和没得到票的人，除此之外他们没有任何其他不同。

yingyinNormal.en: Matthew was co-owner and now his son is. I worked with Matthew. I must work for his boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 马修是共同所有人，如今他儿子是。我曾跟马修共同努力，如今我要为他儿子努力。

yingyinNormal.en: Hold on there, boy. Are you telling me you're the owner of the Bubba Gump Shrimp Corporation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，小兄弟，你是说你就是布巴·甘捕虾公司的老板？

yingyinNormal.en: All right, well, Heather H. Says: The owner stared at me the whole time and didn't blink once.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，希瑟一号说"店主全程都盯着我看眼睛都不眨一下"。

yingyinNormal.en: Jessica K. Says: I told the weird owner that I liked his shirt. He took it off and gave it to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 杰西卡三号说，"我跟变态店主说我喜欢他的衣服结果他立马脱下给我"。
